            <title><![CDATA[Rivals of Aether II adds Gouie on August 4, Mina the Hollower in 2027]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/rivals-of-aether-ii-adds-gouie-on-august-4-mina-the-hollower-in-2027</link>
