            <title><![CDATA[BlazBlue: Central Fiction DLC character Trinity Glassfille revealed]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/blazblue-central-fiction-dlc-character-trinity-glassfille-revealed</link>
            <guid>1563136</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>A key character who has appeared since the early stages of the BlazBlue story.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Following an <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/blazblue-central-fiction-new-dlc-character-announced-for-ps4-pc">initial announcement</a> earlier this week, <a title="Companies > Arc System Works [1,340 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/arc-system-works">Arc System Works</a> has officially announced <em><a title="Games > BlazBlue: Central Fiction [44 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/blazblue-central-fiction">BlazBlue: Central Fiction</a></em> new downloadable content character Trinity Glassfille for the <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a> and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> (<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/586140/BlazBlue_Centralfiction/" target="_blank">Steam</a>) versions of the game. A release date was not announced. <span id="more-1061626"></span></p><p>The announcement reads, “Trinity Glassfille, a key character who has appeared since the early stages of the <em>BlazBlue</em> story, will finally be joining the roster as a playable character. The illustration released today was drawn by the series’ creator, Toshimichi Mori. Stay tuned for further updates regarding the update timing and details!”</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC Character Trinity Glassfille Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="BLAZBLUE CENTRALFICTION - &quot;Trinity Glassfille&quot; Character Reveal" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SFZHNBgQquQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『BLAZBLUE CENTRALFICTION』新規プレイアブルキャラクター「トリニティ＝グラスフィール」参戦決定トレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Riv1TfmWetk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/blazblue-central-fiction-dlc-character-trinity-glassfille-revealed]]></content:encoded>
